At 9.30 in the fellowship hall for breakfast and Sunday school,

00:42:37.730 --> 00:42:40.926
and then at 11 a.m. for our Lord's Day worship service.

00:42:41.469 --> 00:42:42.695
We hope that you have a great week.

00:42:43.117 --> 00:42:44.082
